  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of NYX-783 in Subjects With Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of NYX-783 in Subjects With Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder</official_title>
  <sponsors>
